title: Cheesy Chicken & Guac Sandos with Tomato & Monterey Jack
description: Looking for a delicious, satisfying lunch in just ten minutes? Get ready for the midday repast of your dreams. Close your eyes and picture soft brioche buns slathered with rich guacamole and filled with warm Mexican-spiced chicken layered with melted Monterey Jack cheese and juicy sliced tomato. Nope, it’s not a noontime fever dream—it’s another delicious lunch idea for which you’ll only need to add a napkin (or three!).
